FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1772745123
OL,3,CCompany admits supplying water that
OL,4,Cwas unfit for human consumption
OL,6,FIn a hearing at Exeter magistrates
OL,7,Fcourt today (March 4), South West
OL,8,FWater admitted a charge brought by the
OL,9,FDrinking Water Inspectorate (DWI).
OL,11,FA Government minister welcomed the
OL,12,Fguilty plea describing it as a
OL,13,F"crucial step toward accountability",
OL,14,Fwhile branding the contamination of
OL,15,Fwater as "utterly unacceptable."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1772745123
OL,3,CCompany admits supplying water that
OL,4,Cwas unfit for human consumption
OL,6,FThe full charge said: "Between March
OL,7,F31st and June 1st 2024, at Brixham,
OL,8,Fwere the water undertaker whose supply
OL,9,Fsystem was used for the purposes of
OL,10,Fsupplying water to premises within
OL,11,FLittlehempston water supply zone, and
OL,12,Fthat water was unfit for human
OL,13,Fconsumption."
OL,15,FSouth West Water was prosecuted by the
OL,16,FDWI and faces a fine when it is
OL,17,Fsentenced on 2 June at the same court.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1772745123
OL,3,CCompany admits supplying water that
OL,4,Cwas unfit for human consumption
OL,6,FCaroline Voaden, whose South Devon
OL,7,Fconstituency covers the Brixham area,
OL,8,Fsaid she was glad the company had
OL,9,F"owned up to their serious failures".
OL,11,FShe said: "This time last year, the
OL,12,Fformer South West Water CEO claimed
OL,13,Fcustomers were among the company's top
OL,14,Fpriorities. Today, they have pleaded
OL,15,Fguilty to supplying water unfit for
OL,16,Fhuman consumption.
OL,26,@sD@KOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1772745123
OL,3,CCompany admits supplying water that
OL,4,Cwas unfit for human consumption
OL,6,F"This admission of guilt has been a
OL,7,Flong time coming. I am glad that South
OL,8,FWest Water has owned up to their
OL,9,Fserious failures. This awful event
OL,10,Fshould never have happened.
OL,12,F"But the mismatch between rhetoric and
OL,13,Faction plagues our broken water
OL,14,Findustry. Whether it is protecting
OL,15,Fcustomers or the environment, too many
OL,16,Fwater firms say one thing, then do
OL,17,Fanother."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1772745123
OL,3,CCompany admits supplying water that
OL,4,Cwas unfit for human consumption
OL,6,FThe Lib Dem MP added: "I want to thank
OL,7,Fthe Drinking Water Inspectorate for
OL,8,Fbringing the case and the many
OL,9,Fcampaigners who worked tirelessly to
OL,10,Fensure the anguish they felt during
OL,11,Fthe cryptosporidium outbreak was not
OL,12,Fforgotten.
OL,14,F"Last summer, the government finally
OL,15,Fstarted to overhaul our water industry
OL,16,Fby promising to abolish Ofwat. But
OL,17,Fprogress has been glacially slow. They
OL,18,Fmust go much further and faster ` this
OL,19,Findustry must be properly regulated
OL,20,Fand held to account."
OL,26,@nD@WOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1772745123
OL,3,CCompany admits supplying water that
OL,4,Cwas unfit for human consumption
OL,6,FIn a statement, DEFRA's Water
OL,7,FMinister, Emma Hardy MP, said:
OL,8,F"Contamination of drinking water is
OL,9,Frare - but it is utterly unacceptable.
OL,11,F"The communities affected by this
OL,12,Fabhorrent incident in Brixham deserve
OL,13,Fanswers, and today's guilty plea is a
OL,14,Fcrucial step toward accountability.
OL,16,F"I thank the DWI for their thorough
OL,17,Finvestigation and for their ongoing
OL,18,Fwork to protect public health and
OL,19,Fensure that our drinking water is
OL,20,Fsafe".
OL,26,@pD@AOU|D@EO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
