OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1772745123
OL,3,CCompany admits supplying water that
OL,4,Cwas unfit for human consumption
OL,6,FA spokesperson for South West Water
OL,7,Fsaid: "We want to reiterate our full
OL,8,Fand unreserved apology for the impact
OL,9,Fof the incident in the Brixham area in
OL,10,F2024.
OL,12,F"We have co-operated fully with the
OL,13,FDrinking Water Inspectorate throughout
OL,14,Fits investigations. Today is another
OL,15,Fstage of this legal process which we
OL,16,Fwill continue to support."
OL,18,FIn total the outbreak cost South West
OL,19,FWater #16.3 million in compensation it
OL,20,Fhad to pay to affected customers.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1772745123
OL,3,CCompany admits supplying water that
OL,4,Cwas unfit for human consumption
OL,6,FThe company then pledged a #1.2
OL,7,Fmillion fund to try and help tourism
OL,8,Frecover over the three years,
OL,9,Ffollowing the reputational damage
OL,10,Fcaused by the outbreak.
OL,12,FOver the eight weeks, more than 1,000
OL,13,FSouth West Water network technicians,
OL,14,Fengineers, water quality scientists
OL,15,Fand contractors worked on rotation 24
OL,16,Fhours-a-day to try and resolve the
OL,17,Fproblem.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1772745123
OL,3,CCompany admits supplying water that
OL,4,Cwas unfit for human consumption
OL,6,FOver 34km of water pipes needed to be
OL,7,Fflushed 27 times at high velocity to
OL,8,Fclean network pipes and remove
OL,9,Fcryptosporidium. They also carried out
OL,10,F17 phases of ice-pigging and swabbing
OL,11,F` a more aggressive cleaning approach.
OL,13,FWhat is cryptosporidium?
OL,15,FCryptosporidium is a microscopic
OL,16,Fparasite that causes infections
OL,17,Faffecting both people and farm animals.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
