OL,6,FIt can be found in rivers, untreated
OL,7,Fdrinking water and occasionally in
OL,8,Fswimming pools throughout the UK.You
OL,9,Fcan contract cryptosporidiosis (the
OL,10,Finfection caused by Cryptosporidium)
OL,11,Fdirectly from another person or animal
OL,12,Fby coming into contact with faeces and
OL,13,Fthen touching your mouth without
OL,14,Fthorough handwashing.
OL,16,FThe main symptoms of infection include:
